Class ApplicationUpdateRequest

java.lang.Object
com.atu.green_global_initiative_api.model.dao.request.ApplicationUpdateRequest
public class ApplicationUpdateRequest extends Object
Request DTO for updating an existing application in the Green Global Initiative API. This class contains the necessary fields to update an application.
